  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "COLORado M Solo static wash light takes the optics of the COLORado 1 Solo and shrinks them into a more compact, but equally robust package. Superbly suited for touring and production work indoors or out, this powerful RGBW LED wash light projects an even, fully homogenized beam through fast and smooth zooming optics. It utilizes IP rated power and data connectors as well as full convection cooling for silent and reliable operation, even in the tightest of spaces.\n\nFeatures:\n\n- Zooming RGBW LED wash for touring, rental and production indoors or out\n- Completely homogenized wash with superior color mixing and zoom\n- 5° to 24° smooth and fast zoom\n- All environment operation with IP rated power and DMX connections\n- Color temperature presets, from 3,200 K to 10,000 K\n- Selectable, smooth dimming curves for programming versatility\n- OLED display with password protection",
    "beamType": "Wash",
